	<content><![CDATA[const maxBy = (arr, fn) => Math.max(...arr.map(typeof fn === 'function' ? fn : val => val[fn]));]]></content>
	<description>Returns the maximum value of an array, after mapping each element to a value using the provided function.  Use `Array.map()` to map each element to the value returned by `fn`, `Math.max()` to get the maximum value.</description>
